{"tid":2392936,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國中生因成績不好欲跳樓輕生 警以「自己高考零分」成功救人","createTime":"2021-02-03T06:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T06:37:32.000Z","uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e42f16aa3607cf1a16352af4d75b209720d0b54","tid":2392936,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:23:38.000Z","msg":"國中生因成績不好欲跳樓輕生 警以「自己高考零分」成功救人<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/02/02/1/11464361.jpeg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=465&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F02%2F02%2F1%2F11464361.jpeg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D465%26nt%3D1&h=5a7ef585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日在中國大陸的安徽淮南，一名女國中生因為成績不好想跳樓輕生，而在場的警察以先前自己高考零分舉例相勸，成功救下女孩。<br />\n<br />\n事發在1月31日傍晚，當地警方接到報案，某建築物的26樓頂樓有人企圖跳樓。當警察趕到現場發現，一名女學生懸坐頂樓邊緣上，情緒失控正在哭泣。當時情況危急，警察不停安慰女學生並慢慢靠近。得知她因考試成績不好有了輕生想法後，在場一名警察車勸說「我高考考了零分」，引起對方注意，另一名警察則趁機把女學生從邊緣抱下來，施救成功。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，欲輕生的女孩是國中三年級學生，下午三時左右就坐在樓頂，一直沒人發現，警察把她送回家時，父母毫不知情。警察將情況告知其家人後，經教育和溝通，女孩對輕生行為感到後悔，父母也表示會反思"},{"pid":"13afc86ae0934d5e6eab6f848994fafd93c41baa","tid":2392936,"uid":191579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a625d349e1d713bd8173c86d0ff309aacb1d77b5","tid":2392936,"uid":311198,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:25:03.000Z","msg":"香港嗰啲毅進 都可以發揮相同作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae645cfc4b46545bc24548dd4a2deda40807de9","tid":2392936,"uid":273953,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"香港會仲想跳樓<br />\n成績唔好就要做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111b9c43430fdb5886cf5cfd1af06d060883651a","tid":2392936,"uid":50894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"ekids三個加埋都都係得1分"},{"pid":"c0ab966e555d9978ee1a1f92d417feb595712cdb","tid":2392936,"uid":136416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a625d349e1d713bd8173c86d0ff309aacb1d77b5","tid":2392936,"uid":311198,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:25:03.000Z","msg":"香港嗰啲毅進 都可以發揮相同作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:37:32.000Z","msg":"但唔發揮<br />\n推人落樓"}]}